OL,5, The boss of a US mortgage company, who 
OL,6, fired hundreds of his staff in a Zoom  
OL,7, meeting has said he is "deeply sorry"  
OL,8, for the way the lay-offs were handled. 
OL,10,FThe sackings were necessary said Vishal
OL,11,FGarg, but he accepted he had "blundered
OL,12,Fthe execution" and "embarrassed" them. 
OL,14,F"I failed to show the appropriate      
OL,15,Famount of respect and appreciation for 
OL,16,Fthe individuals who were affected," he 
OL,17,Fsaid in a letter on the firm's website.
OL,19,FMr Garg was heavily criticised after he
OL,20,Fsacked 900 staff in an online meeting. 
